{"id":584696,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/05/【对比新闻】gap-为地图t恤道歉-vs-中国人在越南穿南海/","date":"2018-05-15T07:01:27Z","modified":"2018-05-15T07:05:40Z","title":"【对比新闻】GAP为地图T恤道歉 vs 国人在越南穿南海九段线","content":"<p><strong>【编者注】</strong>遭中国“爱国”群众抗议的GAP地图T恤只在部分海外市场销售，并未出现在中国市场。而这些身穿在南海周边国家极具争议性的南海九段线地图的爱国群众，却是真的身在越南。<strong>这大概就是战狼逻辑。</strong></p>\n<p>据越南当地媒体<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ngaphambbc/status/995952335586291718\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">报道</a>，2018年5月13日晚11点半左右，有人在金兰国际机场目睹<strong>十位中国女子，穿着印有在越南极具争议性的南海九段线地图的T恤等待入境</strong>。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/DdGL6lOX4AAsQIg.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-584706\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/DdGL6lOX4AAsQIg.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"425\" height=\"567\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/DdGL6lOX4AAsQIg.jpg 720w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/DdGL6lOX4AAsQIg-225x300.jpg 225w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 425px) 100vw, 425px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/DdGL6vwWAAEBy1I.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-584707\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/DdGL6vwWAAEBy1I.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"425\" height=\"567\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/DdGL6vwWAAEBy1I.jpg 720w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/DdGL6vwWAAEBy1I-225x300.jpg 225w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 425px) 100vw, 425px\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">After passports embossed with the 9-dash line, some  tourists from <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/China?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#China</a> now wear T-shirts with the controversial drawings. A contact of mine sent me these photos of Chinese visitors at an unspecified airport in <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/Vietnam?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#Vietnam</a>. Not sure how authorities reacted! <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/SouthChinaSea?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#SouthChinaSea</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/vT5e07XqYi\">pic.twitter.com/vT5e07XqYi</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; Nga Pham (@ngaphambbc) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/ngaphambbc/status/995730848036073472?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">May 13, 2018</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<h3><span style=\"color: #333333;\">VS</span><br />\n<strong><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.dw.com/zh/t%E6%81%A4%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%9C%B0%E5%9B%BE%E6%83%B9%E4%BA%89%E8%AE%AE-gap%E5%BE%AE%E5%8D%9A%E9%81%93%E6%AD%89/a-43786880?&amp;zhongwen=simp\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">德国之声 | T恤中国地图惹争议 GAP微博道歉</a></strong></h3>\n<blockquote><p>美国服饰零售商盖璞 (GAP)14日晚间为了一件T恤在官方微博上道歉。</p>\n<p>“盖璞集团尊重中国的主权和领土完整。我们获知在个别海外市场发售的一款GapT恤上的中国地图设计有误。我们对这一无意的失误感到万分抱歉。”</p>\n<p>一名网友在中国社交媒体网络微博上发布了一件T恤衫的照片，他说中国的领土，包括藏南，台湾和南中国海在地图上被遗漏。他说T恤的照片是在加拿大的一家直营店所拍摄。</p>\n<p>GAP发出道歉声明并强调，“该款产品已从中国市场撤回并全部销毁。”</p></blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/5afa60ccf296ad0244a3d2b0_201805151223.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-584703\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/5afa60ccf296ad0244a3d2b0_201805151223.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"558\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/5afa60ccf296ad0244a3d2b0_201805151223.jpg 479w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/5afa60ccf296ad0244a3d2b0_201805151223-242x300.jpg 242w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/5afa606af296ad0244a3d2ae_201805151222.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-584704\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/5afa606af296ad0244a3d2ae_201805151222.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"525\" height=\"402\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/5afa606af296ad0244a3d2ae_201805151222.jpg 588w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/5afa606af296ad0244a3d2ae_201805151222-300x230.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 525px) 100vw, 525px\" /></a></p>\n","author":980,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,27949],"tags":[16478,30038,10268,33704,8646,23802,9481,30519]}